data.description: HILLWOOD---Lovely home in the desirable Hillwood neighborhood. In this home you will find a formal dining room, an office/library, a spacious kitchen, with gas stove, breakfast room with large pantry, and a separate laundry/mudroom. A comfortable family room with fireplace and vaulted ceiling overlooks the sparkling pool, patio, brand new deck, and, fenced backyard. This home has four bedrooms and two bathrooms. The main bedroom includes a large walk-in closet and en suite bath with shower and luxurious jetted tub. The additional three bedrooms have plenty of closet space, and the hall bathroom includes a large linen closet.  A two-car carport also has a storage room. PLUS! A cozy guest cottage with one bedroom and one bathroom will make any guest feel welcome! The cottage has a kitchenette and large sitting room, an additional room that can be used as another bedroom, and a large walk-in closet with washer/dryer hookup.  The cottage is approximately 600 square feet and is included in the total sf.  Make your appointment today!
